True if the connection is valid.

connect(bytes32,bytes32,string,string).notice: connect - Creates a directed edge between two kinds with a relation and transform.

consumers(bytes32).notice: consumers - Returns all transforms that consume (have edges from) a given kind.

defineKind(string,string).notice: define - Registers a new kind in the taxonomy.

dependents(bytes32).notice: dependents - Returns all kinds that depend on (are downstream of) a given kind.

graph().notice: graph - Returns the complete kind taxonomy graph.

producers(bytes32).notice: producers - Returns all transforms that produce (have edges to) a given kind.

route(bytes32,bytes32).notice: route - Finds a path between two kinds using breadth-first search.

validate(bytes32,bytes32).notice: validate - Validates that a connection between two kinds is valid.
